subSubSection.paragraph:
All specimens of the new species were collected from the areas with mixed forests of coniferous and broadleaved trees. Some specimens were collected by using a sweeping net mainly from pine trees, while a few of them were also found on lower vegetations (
Figs. 19–20
). In addition, some specimens were collected by using Mercury- Vapor light trap.
